# =======================================================
# PRODUCTION MIGRATION NOTES:
# =======================================================
# Before going to production:
# 1. Set ENVIRONMENT=production
# 2. Set DEBUG=false
# 3. Set MAINNET_ENABLED=true (when ready)
# 4. Replace SECRET_KEY with secure random key
# 5. Use mainnet RPC URLs with your API keys
# 6. Configure real alerting (email/telegram)
# 7. Set appropriate position/loss limits
# 8. Enable SENTRY_DSN for error tracking
